    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SystemExitStatus>

    public enum SystemExitStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<SystemExitStatus>
    Represents a status System.exit(int) can be called with.
    Version:
    1.2
    Author:
    Joshua Gleitze

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      ALL
      System.exit(x) with any argument x.
      EXACTLY
      System.exit(x) with a x that has to be specified through status(int).
      NONE
      No call to System.exit(x) at all.
      WITH_0
      System.exit(0).
      WITH_GREATER_THAN_0
      System.exit(x) with x>0.
